chapters.title: What is the Bible composed of?
There are three things every book must have, what are they?
Who is the author of the Bible? [2 Peter 1:21, Jeremiah 30:2]
What are the four things the Bible is "good" for? [2 Timothy 3:16-17]
The Apostle Paul encourages us to do what, in order to understand truth? [2 Timothy 2:15; Psalms 55:17]
When one begins to read God's Book what two fold-fold effect will it have ON upon them. [Revelation 10:10]
Why do some people have difficulty understanding Bible truth? [Mark 7:8]
What attitude is essential in understanding Bible truth? 1 John 1:7; John 2:5
